<paragraph blockId="4.[189,573,813,839]" box="[189,573,813,839]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
Afrotropical Region (see 
<figureCitation box="[488,559,813,839]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="4.[189,232,1964,1990]" captionTargetBox="[189,1399,1526,1935]" captionTargetId="figure@4.[189,1399,1525,1935]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="Fig. 2. Known distribution of Afrosyrphus varipes Curran, 1927 (red triangles) and Afrosyrphus schmuttereri sp. nov. (black circles)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3778833" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3778833/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Fig. 2</figureCitation>
